## Deploy

Configure the control-plane URL and deploy token once:

```bash
pt configure --addr http://127.0.0.1:18080 --token
pt deploy
pt claim
```

CI may use `PLUMTREE_SERVER_URL` and `PLUMTREE_DEV_TOKEN` as temporary
environment overrides instead of changing the saved user configuration.

After the first claim, later deploys (locally or from CI) reuse the deploy id in
`.plumtree/deploy.json` to update the same app.
